It's probably the Multi4 DVD (IT/GR/PT/ES), GR=Greek

There was a scene release for this Multi4 DVD:
Pro.Evolution.Soccer.2011.Multi4.READNFO-iTWINS

There is also a Multi7 DVD (EN/FR/DE/IT/GR/PT/ES) that includes all the languages:
Pro_Evolution_Soccer_2011_MULTI_DVD_PC-R55
This release combines the 3 scene releases (RELOADED, GENESIS, ITWINS). From the included screenshots (r55-pes2011-proofa.jpg, r55-pes2011-proofb.jpg), it seems it supports both Greek text and audio. In fact for all 7 languages it has text and audio. 

A torrent (uploaded by VIP member Morck22) for the Multi7 DVD can be found in:
